  <titleInfo>
    <title>Rock House Holiness Church service, 1998 June 21</title>
  </titleInfo>
  <abstract>Video recording opens with Lydia "Bugs" Hollins and two others leading a congregation of sixty-five in song. The service also features extended serpent handling and preaching by John Wayne "Punkin" Brown Jr., Billy Summerford, and Bill Pelfry. Several women congregants handle serpents, including Nola Faye Roberts, Lydia "Bugs" Hollins, and elderly twins. Joyce Summerford's singing is also featured.</abstract>
